<p><strong>Interface Development</strong></p>
<p><strong>GADDIEL </strong>has strong strength in developing interfaces to migrate and port custom data, legacy data and transfer of data between disparate systems.  Interfacing is done for the Custom Applications and Web applications as part of customizations and enhancements.</p>



